{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 78,
  "title": "第七十八章（任信）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下莫柔弱於水，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而攻堅強者莫之能勝，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以其無以易之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "弱之勝強，"
    },
    {
      "text": "柔之勝剛，"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下莫不知，"
    },
    {
      "text": "莫能行。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人云："
    },
    {
      "text": "受國之垢，是謂社稷主；"
    },
    {
      "text": "受國不祥，是為天下王。"
    },
    {
      "text": "正言若反。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "圓中則圓，方中則方，壅之則止，決之則行。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "水能懷山襄陵，磨鐵消銅，莫能勝水而成功也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫攻堅強者，無以易於水。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "水能滅火，陰能消陽。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "舌柔齒剛，齒先舌亡。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "知柔弱者久長，剛強者折傷。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "恥謙卑，好強梁。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂下事也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君能受國之垢濁者，若江海不逆小流，則能長保其社稷，為一國之君主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君能引過自與，代民受不祥之殃，則可以王天下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此乃正直之言，世人不知，以為反言。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
